  "subject": "Provide selected v1 endpoints accessible in backward compatible manner",
  "commit_message": "Provide selected v1 endpoints accessible in backward compatible manner\n\nDepending on configfile option `preserve-v1-backward-compatibility`,\nstart k8splugin in normal or backward compatible mode\n(setting broker handler and healthcheck to listen on /, /v1, /v1/v1).\nBy default, backward compatibility is turned off.\n\nIssue-ID: MULTICLOUD-1053\nSigned-off-by: Konrad Bańka <k.banka@samsung.com>\nChange-Id: I734fb7206db6fb20c9d108fc201207eecdc619e5\n",
